      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING DALY (1) has been on speed at the last couple here and fought on to hit the frame, last outing finishing third beaten 2 lengths (23.73). Well placed and gets his chance. TIGER TAILS (4) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when second (22.64) in a Grade 5 over 388m at Gosford. Good beginner who will be prominent from trap one. Can hit the frame this time. TRICKLE (2) finished third (23.06) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 6th at Gosford. Has a good record here at this journey. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Must be included in calculations. KENNY'S GIRL (7) can run a bold race on best form.",
